In the Matter of the Application of John T. Sullivan et al. against Edward Corsi, as Industrial Commissioner of the State of New York, et al.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied, with ten dollars costs. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ. [See 268 App. Div. 1037.]
